Paper: hep-th/0206218

Date: 2002-06-24

Title: On marginal deformation of WZNW model and PP-wave limit of deformed

$AdS_{3}\times S^{3}$ string geometryAuthors: Ruben Manvelyan

Comments: 10 pages, latex

We discuss the Penrose limit of the classical string geometry obtained from atruly marginal deformation of $SL(2)\otimes SU(2)$ WZNW model.